comparison_points.our_benefit: Solid steel, matte black attachments stay rigid under heavy loads and daily use
comparison_points.competitor_issue: Cheaper hollow bars bend, chip and feel flimsy after a few workouts

comparison_points.our_benefit: Rubber-grip handles and contoured shapes improve comfort and secure grip
comparison_points.competitor_issue: Bare metal or thin foam grips slip, rotate and dig into hands during sets

comparison_points.our_benefit: Universal metal eyelet hardware clips quickly to any cable machine setup
comparison_points.competitor_issue: Narrow or poorly welded rings don’t fit carabiners and can snap under tension

comparison_points.our_benefit: Rust-resistant black powder-coated finish keeps your home gym looking clean
comparison_points.competitor_issue: Uncoated chrome or paint flakes, rusts and leaves metal residue on hands
